<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
        <main>
            <section class="page-header">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1>Our Vision & Mission</h1>
                    <p>Guiding principles that illuminate our path towards educational excellence and societal impact.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="content-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row" style="display: flex; gap: 50px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                        <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px;">
                            <h2 style="color: var(--primary-blue);">Our Vision</h2>
                            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-gold); font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">A Future
                                Transformed by Education</h3>
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Nageshwaram Foundation Trust envisions a vibrant and
                                equitable society where every individual, particularly from rural backgrounds, has
                                access to empowering educational opportunities. We aspire to create a generation of
                                confident, skilled, and ethically conscious citizens who are capable of driving positive
                                change in their communities and the nation.</p>
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">We see our institutions as centers of excellence, not just
                                in academics but in holistic development, where traditional values blend seamlessly with
                                modern pedagogical approaches. We aim to inspire a lifelong love for learning, preparing
                                students not just for careers, but for meaningful lives.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px;">
                            <div
                                style="background: var(--bg-cream); padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-gold);">
                                <h2 style="color: var(--primary-blue);">Our Mission</h2>
                                <h3 style="color: var(--accent-gold); font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">Nurturing
                                    Minds, Building Character</h3>
                                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">To realize our vision, Nageshwaram Foundation Trust is
                                    committed to:</p>
                                <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0;">
                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 15px;"><i class="fas fa-check text-gold"
                                            style="margin-right: 10px;"></i><strong>Providing Quality
                                            Education:</strong> Establishing and supporting educational institutions
                                        that offer a comprehensive, balanced, and relevant curriculum from foundational
                                        learning to advanced studies.</li>
                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 15px;"><i class="fas fa-check text-gold"
                                            style="margin-right: 10px;"></i><strong>Fostering Holistic
                                            Development:</strong> Implementing programs that enhance intellectual,
                                        physical, emotional, and spiritual well-being.</li>
                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 15px;"><i class="fas fa-check text-gold"
                                            style="margin-right: 10px;"></i><strong>Promoting Inclusivity:</strong>
                                        Ensuring equitable access to education for all children, especially those from
                                        marginalized sections of society.</li>
                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 15px;"><i class="fas fa-check text-gold"
                                            style="margin-right: 10px;"></i><strong>Empowering Educators:</strong>
                                        Recruiting and training dedicated teachers who are passionate about nurturing
                                        young minds.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="call-to-action">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2>Join Our Journey</h2>
                    <p>Together, we can achieve our vision of a better tomorrow, shaped by enlightened minds and strong
                        characters.</p>
                    <a href="/institutions" class="cta-button primary">Explore Our Institutions</a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>